                  <figcaption class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <span class="inline-block bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Slika 14B</span>
                    <span class="block mt-2 text-gray-700">Precjepljivanje bakterijske kulture na sterilni kosi agar</span>
